ArchSetup - setup script for Arch Linux
=======================================

Script for configuring my arch installation.

Will install suckless tools (dwm, dmenu, st, slstatus and slock),
together with a handfull of other software and tools that I use.

* CURRENTLY WORK IN PROGRESS, USE AT OWN RISK *

How to use:
1. git clone the repo
2. cd into archomatic
3. run ./install.sh

Requirements
------------
A minimal base install of Arch Linux

